Package org.wikidata.wdtk.examples

Package for example programs that demonstrate how to use Wikidata Toolkit in practice.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DumpProcessingExample
    This class demonstrates how to write an application that downloads and processes dumpfiles from Wikidata.org.
    ExampleHelpers
    Class for sharing code that is used in many examples.
    RdfSerializationExample
    This class shows how convert data from wikidata.org to RDF in N3 format.
    SerializationExample
    This class shows how convert data from wikidata.org to the JSON format as used in the Wikibase API.
    SitelinksExample
    This class demonstrates how to get access to information about sitelinks in Wikidata.org.
